  "rationale": "<p>Choice C is correct. The lines y = 4x + 2 and y = 4x - 5 have equal slopes (4) but different y-intercepts (2 and -5), so they are parallel and never intersect \u2014 the system has no solution. Choice A has identical lines (infinitely many solutions). Choice B has lines that intersect at (0, 1). Choice D has lines that intersect at (0, 7).</p>",
